# Workflow: Create New API Route

## Goal
Create a secure and functional API endpoint.

## Steps
1. Define endpoint purpose
2. Choose HTTP method
3. Create route file in `/app/api`
4. Use API Route Scaffolder skill
5. Validate request input
6. Implement logic
7. Add error handling
8. Return structured response
9. Test with Postman or frontend

## Checklist
- [ ] Input validated
- [ ] Errors handled safely
- [ ] No sensitive leaks
- [ ] Correct status codes
- [ ] Works end-to-end

## Output
A production-ready API route